      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 1 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 1 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九，潛龍，勿用。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the first (or lowest) NINE, undivided, (we see its subject as) the dragon lying hid (in the deep). It is not the time for active doing.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
