      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 1 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 1 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二，見龍在田，利見大人。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the second NINE, undivided, (we see its subject as) the dragon appearing in the field. It will be advantageous to meet with the great man.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
