      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 1 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 1 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五，飛龍在天，利見大人。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the fifth NINE, undivided, (we see its subject as) the dragon on the wing in the sky. It will be advantageous to meet with the great man</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
