      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 1 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 1 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九，亢龍，有悔。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the sixth (or topmost) NINE, undivided, (we see its subject as) the dragon exceeding the proper limits. There will be occasion for repentance.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
